description: For every entry in a custom list, make an artifact in a container containing the columns as cef fields.

inputs.description: The name of the custom list to make artifacts.
inputs.name: custom_list_name

inputs.description: The container in which to put the new artifacts.
inputs.name: container_id

inputs.description: Supply a list of values here to override the headers. If set to False, then it will use generic col+N headers. E.g. [col1, col2, col3, ...]
inputs.name: headers

inputs.description: If desired, the new artifacts can have a custom artifact name. Defaults to "Artifact from <custom_list_name>"
inputs.name: artifact_name
